        <mi>B</mi>
        <mi>C</mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle BC}</annotati=
on>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/74e0f24a49061dcd63874f7d81f395b5f38800f7" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:3.53ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle BC}"=
></span> is the diameter of a circle and <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mw=
e-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathm=
l-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math=
/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle A}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
