        <mi>A</mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle A}</annotatio=
n>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/7daff47fa58cdfd29dc333def748ff5fa4c923e3" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:1.743ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle A}"=
></span> is any other point on the circle, then <span class=3D"mwe-math-ele=
ment mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-mat=
h-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/19=
